{
  "chapter": "109",
  "title": "李将军列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "出身与初仕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成纪</span>人。他的先祖叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李信</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时为将领，就是追获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>的那位。李氏原居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槐里</span>，后徙居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成纪</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>家世代传习射艺。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入侵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">萧关</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>以良家<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的身份从军<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>匈奴，因精于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">骑射</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>敌斩首缴获很多，被任为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中郎</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的堂弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李蔡</span>也任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>，都做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武骑常侍</span>，俸禄<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">八百石</span>。曾经跟随皇帝出行，遇到冲锋陷阵抵挡关隘、格斗<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">猛兽</span>的场合，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"可惜啊，您生不逢时！若您生在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>时代，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>侯哪在话下！\""
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "孝景时任边郡太守",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>初即位时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陇西都尉</span>，调任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑郎将</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>叛乱时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骁骑都尉</span>，跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周亚夫\">亚夫（周亚夫）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>敌旗，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>城下显露功名。因为接受了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁王</span>授予的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，回朝后，朝廷没有奖赏。调任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上谷太守</span>，每天都与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>交<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">典属国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙昆邪</span>向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>哭诉说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>的才气，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">天下无双</span>，自恃其能，屡次与敌虏交<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，恐怕会失去他。\" 于是便调他做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上郡太守</span>。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>转任边郡<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>，调到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上郡</span>。他曾任<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北地</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代郡</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中太守</span>，都以力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>闻名。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "射雕者与解鞍示不走",
      "text": "<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入侵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上郡</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中贵人</span>跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>训练兵士以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中贵人</span>率骑兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十</span>人纵马驰骋，遇见<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>，与之交<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>回身射箭，射伤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中贵人</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>他的骑兵几乎殆尽。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中贵人</span>逃到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>处。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"这必定是射<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">雕</span>的人。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>于是率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百骑</span>前去追击那<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>失去<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>徒步行走，已走出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十里</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>命令他的骑兵展开左右两翼，亲自射击那<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>其<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，活捉<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，果然是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>的射<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">雕</span>者。他将其捆绑好扶上<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，望见<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千骑</span>，看见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，以为是诱敌骑，都惊骇，上山布阵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百骑</span>都大为恐惧，想策马驰回。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"我们离大军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十里</span>，如今就这样以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百骑</span>逃走，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>追射我们立刻就全部没命了。现在我们留下来，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>必定以为我们是大军诱饵，必不敢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>我们。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>命令众骑：\"前进！\" 前进到距<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>阵地不到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二里</span>的地方，停下，命令：\"都下<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>解<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span>！\" 骑兵说：\"虏众多且近，如有紧急，怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"那些敌虏以为我们会逃走，现在都解下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span>表示不走，用以坚定他们的判断。\" 于是胡骑便不敢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>。有一个骑白<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>的将领出来监护他的部队，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>上<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>与<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀骑</span>奔驰射<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>那胡将，又返回自己骑兵中，解下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span>，命<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵都纵<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>躺卧。此时正值傍晚，胡兵始终奇怪，不敢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夜半</span>时，胡兵还以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝在旁有伏军想夜里<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>他们，胡人便都领兵而去。天亮时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>才返回他的大军。大军不知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>所处位置，所以没有接应。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "为卫尉与程不识治军之异",
      "text": "过了很久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>，左右近臣以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>是名将，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上郡太守</span>升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">未央卫尉</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>也做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长乐卫尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>从前与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>都以边<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>身份领兵屯驻。等出<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>胡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>行军没有部曲行阵，就着水草好处扎营，休止时人人自便，不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀</span>斗自卫，军幕府省去繁琐文书簿籍之事，然而也远派斥候，所以未曾遭遇危害。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>严正地部署部曲行伍、驻营布阵，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀</span>斗，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>吏处理军中文书细致分明，军队得不到休息，但也从未遭遇危害。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：程不识\">不识（程不识）</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>治军极为简易，然而若敌虏突然来犯，他无法抵御；而他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒也安逸快乐，都乐于为他效死。我军虽繁琐扰民，然而敌虏也不能侵犯我。\" 当时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝边郡的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>都是名将，然而<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>惧怕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>的谋略，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒也多乐于跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>而苦于跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程不识</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>时因多次直谏做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span>。为人廉洁，谨守<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文法</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "马邑之谋与被俘脱逃",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝用<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>城诱骗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，派大军埋伏在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>旁谷中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骁骑将军</span>，归属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军将军</span>指挥。当时<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>察觉了，退走，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军都没有功劳。此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span>身份为将军，出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>兵多，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军，活捉了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>素闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>贤能，下令说：\"得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>必须生擒送来。\" 胡骑俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>当时受伤生病，他们把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>放在两<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>之间，用绳网载着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>躺着。走了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀里</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>装死，斜眼看旁边有一胡人少年骑着骏<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>突然腾起跳上胡少年的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，顺势把那少年推落，夺<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span>打<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>向南驰走<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十里</span>，找到了剩余的部队，就引军入塞。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>派<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百</span>骑追赶，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>一路<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>胡少年的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>，射<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>追骑，因此得以脱身。于是回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>交给法吏审判。法吏判<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>所失亡人马很多，又被敌虏生擒，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "霸陵尉辱与为右北平太守",
      "text": "不久，家居<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>家和前<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">颍阴侯</span>的孙子屏居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南山</span>中射猎。曾经夜间带一骑出行，跟人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>饮酒。回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span>亭时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>醉了，呵止<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的骑从说：\"这是以前的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李将军</span>。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>说：\"现任的将军都不得夜行，何况是过去的！\" 扣留<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>宿于亭下。没过多久，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>入侵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辽西太守</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩将军</span>，此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩将军</span>调驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>便召<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右北平太守</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>立即请把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>一起带去，到了军中就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩</span>了他。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "飞将军威名",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>听说后，称他为\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的飞将军\"，避开他<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，不敢入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "射石入石",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>外出打猎，看见草中的石头，误以为是<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>而射它，箭头没入石中，看时才知是石。又再射，始终不能射入石中了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>所在郡听说有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>，常自己去射。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>射<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>腾起伤了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>也终于射<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "为人与治军",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>廉洁，得到赏赐就分给他的部下，饮食与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒同享。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>一生做<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>官<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四十多年（时长）</span>，家无余财，终其一生也不谈家产之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>身材高大，猿臂善射，这也是天性，即使他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>和他人来学，都不能赶上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>寡言少语，和人在一起时画地作军阵，以射中宽窄的靶子饮酒。专以射为戏，至死不变。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>带兵，在缺水缺粮的地方，看见水源，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒未饮尽，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>不近水；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒未吃完，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>不尝食。他宽缓不苛，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵因此爱戴乐于为他效力。他射箭，见到敌人逼近，非在<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十</span>步之内，估计射不中不发，发射就应弦而倒。因此，他领兵多次被困受辱，他射<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">猛兽</span>也曾被所伤。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "为郎中令与从大将军出征",
      "text": "过了不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石建</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">卒</span>，于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：石建\">建（石建）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中令</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>再任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">後将军</span>，跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>军出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定襄</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。诸将多有斩敌首级达到定额的，以功封侯，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军没有功劳。此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中令</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千骑</span>出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">右北平</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博望侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张骞</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万骑</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>同行，各走一条路。行进了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百里</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左贤王</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万骑</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span>住<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵都惊恐，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>就派他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>去冲击敌阵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>单独率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十骑</span>驰进，直冲胡骑，从其左右穿出而归，告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"胡虏容易对付。\" 军中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵才心安。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>布置圆阵面向外，胡军急<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>，箭下如雨。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵战死的超过半数，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的箭也快用尽。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>便命令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒拉满弓不发，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>亲自用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">大黄</span>弩射敌<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨将</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数人</span>，胡虏的攻势稍解。恰逢<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日暮</span>，将吏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵都面无人色，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>意气自如，更加整饬军容。军中从此佩服他的勇敢。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">第二天</span>，再力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博望侯</span>军也赶到，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>军才解围而去。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军疲惫，不能追击。此时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军几乎全军覆没，返回。按<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>法，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博望侯</span>行军迟误期限，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当死</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军功与损失相抵，没有赏赐。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "李蔡⟦○封侯⟧与相不当侯",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的堂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李蔡</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>都侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李蔡\">蔡（李蔡）</span>积累功劳至<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二千石</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝武帝</span>时，做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代相</span>。在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔五年</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">轻车将车</span>，跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右贤王</span>，立功达定额，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">乐安侯</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩二年</span>中，代替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李蔡\">蔡（李蔡）</span>这人才能在下等中品，名声比<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>差得很远，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>得不到爵位封邑，官位不过<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">九卿</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李蔡\">蔡（李蔡）</span>身为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，官居<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒有的也<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span>得<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封侯</span>之位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>曾与<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">望气</span>者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王朔</span>私下闲谈，说：\"自从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>以来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>没有不在其中的，而各部<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>以下，才能不及中等，但凭<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>胡军功封侯的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>不落人后，却没有尺寸之功得以封邑，这是为什么呢？难道是我的相貌不当封侯吗？还是命该如此？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王朔\">朔（王朔）</span>说：\"将军自己想想，难道曾有过遗憾的事吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"我曾做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">陇西守</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">羌</span>人曾经反叛，我诱降了他们，投降者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百馀人</span>，我用欺诈手段在同一天<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了他们。至今大恨的就这件事。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王朔\">朔（王朔）</span>说：\"灾祸没有大于<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>已降之人的，这就是将军不得封侯的原因啊。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "最后一战",
      "text": "又过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑将军</span>大举出<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>多次请求随行。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>认为他老了，不答应；过了很久才答应，任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">前将军</span>。这一年，是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩四年</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "失道东路",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>既已跟<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，出塞后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>从俘虏口中得知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>所在地，就亲自带精兵前去追击，而令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右将军</span>军合并，出东道。东道稍迂回遥远，而大军所行之路水草稀少，形势不便于大队并行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>自请说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所部为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">前将军</span>，如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>却调<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>出东道，况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>从束发起就与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，今才得一次直接对阵<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>的机会，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愿居前锋，先死战<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>也暗中受<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>告诫，认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广</span>年老，命数不好，不要让他直当<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，恐怕得不到想要的结果。而当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙敖</span>新近失侯，做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中将军</span>跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>也想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙敖\">敖（公孙敖）</span>与自己一同当<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，所以调走<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">前将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>当时知道，坚决向<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>辞谢。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>不听，命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>封好书信送给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的幕府，说：\"速赴所部，按文书行事。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>没有向<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>告辞便出发了，心情非常怨怒地赴部，引兵与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵食其\">食其（赵食其）</span>军合兵出东道。军中没有向导，或者迷了路，落在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>之后。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>交<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>逃走，没能抓到就回军。向南横穿大漠，遇到了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">前将军</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右将军</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>见过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>后，回到军中。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>送干粮浊酒给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>，顺便问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵食其\">食其（赵食其）</span>失道的情形，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>想上书向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>详细禀报军情。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>没回答，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>急促责成<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>到幕府对簿。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>说：\"众<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>无罪，是我自己迷失了道路。我现在就自己去对簿。\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "引刀自刭",
      "text": "到幕府后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>对他的部下说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>自束发以来，与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大小<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>役<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀</span>次，今幸得跟从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>出征而直接与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>接战，但<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>又调<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>的部队走迂回遥远的路，又迷了路，难道不是天意吗！况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>已<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六十馀</span>岁了，终究不能再去面对<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀</span>笔吏。\" 于是引<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀</span>自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刭</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>军中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士大夫</span>全军都哭。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>听说后，认识不认识他的，无论老壮都为他垂泪。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右将军</span>独自被交法吏审判，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当死</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">赎</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "三子与李敢",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span>个儿子，叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李当户\">当户（李当户）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李椒\">椒（李椒）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>，都做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩嫣</span>嬉戏，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩嫣\">嫣（韩嫣）</span>稍微不逊，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李当户\">当户（李当户）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩嫣\">嫣（韩嫣）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩嫣\">嫣（韩嫣）</span>逃走。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李当户\">当户（李当户）</span>勇敢。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李当户\">当户（李当户）</span>早死，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李椒\">椒（李椒）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代郡太守</span>，都先<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李当户\">当户（李当户）</span>有遗腹子名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>死于军中时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>正跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑将军</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>死后次年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李蔡</span>身为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>因侵占<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>陵园周边空地，应交法吏审问，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李蔡\">蔡（李蔡）</span>也自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>，不愿对簿公堂，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李敢</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>身份跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑将军</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>胡<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左贤王</span>，力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>，夺<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左贤王</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼓旗</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>很多，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百户</span>，代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广\">广（李广）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中令</span>。不久，他怨<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>逼死他父亲，就<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>伤<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>隐瞒此事不张扬。过了不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>随<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>地，来到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘泉宫</span>打猎。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>有亲戚关系，射<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>当时正受宠，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>为他掩饰说是<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鹿</span>角触<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>了李敢。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>死。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>有个女儿在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>宫中，受宠幸，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李敢\">敢（李敢）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李禹\">禹（李禹）</span>也受<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>宠爱，但他贪好利益，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">李氏</span>家族渐趋衰微。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "李陵为将",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李陵</span>成年后，被选为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建章监</span>，监率众骑。他善射，爱护<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>认为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">李氏</span>世代为将，就派他率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百骑</span>。他曾深入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千馀里</span>，越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">居延</span>察看地形，没见到敌虏就回来。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑都尉</span>，率<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丹阳</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地人<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>，教练射术于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酒泉</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">张掖</span>以屯兵防备胡。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "李陵降匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">天汉二年</span>秋，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">贰师将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李广利</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万骑</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右贤王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">祁连</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天山</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>率他的射<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>步兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">居延</span>北约<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀里</span>，想以此分散<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>兵力，不让他们专攻<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">贰师</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>到了约定日期就回军，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>率兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八万</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>，兵器箭矢耗尽，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒死者过半，而所<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">杀</span>伤的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>也有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀人</span>。一边撤退一边<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>斗，连<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斗</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八天（时长）</span>，返至离<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">居延</span>还有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀里</span>时，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>阻截窄路断绝退道，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>粮食匮乏、救兵不到，虏急<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击</span>招降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>说：\"无面目报答<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>。\" 就投降了<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。他的部队尽数覆灭，流散逃回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四百馀人</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "李氏败落",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>既已得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>，素闻他家声名，加之他<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战</span>斗勇敢，就把自己的女儿嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>并使之显贵。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝听说后，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">族</span>诛了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">陵（李陵）</span>的母亲妻儿。此后，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">李氏</span>的名声<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>落，而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人曾居李氏门下的都以此为耻。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：传上讲\"其身正，不令而行；其身不正，虽令不从\"。 说的就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李将军</span>吧？我看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李将军</span>，忠厚老实像个乡下人，嘴里说不出巧辩之辞。 等到他死的那天，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>认识他和不认识他的，都为他尽情哀悼。 那是因为他的忠实诚心取信于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士大夫</span>吧？谚语说：\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">桃李不言，下自成蹊</span>\"。 此言虽小，可以比喻大事。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "猿臂善射，实在是自负其能。 解<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞍</span>退敌，圆阵摧破敌锋。 边郡屡任守职，大军再三跟从。 失道被弃，数奇不得封侯。 惋惜啊名将，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">天下无双</span>！"
    }
  }
}